# Frontend (Vite) build-time env. Copy to .env / .env.local and fill in.
# Only VITE_-prefixed vars are exposed to the client bundle.

# Base URL for the API. Empty = same origin (nginx proxies /api on the droplet).
VITE_API_BASE=

# Dev mode. Gates development-only affordances: the skin picker (bottom-left),
# the build stamp (bottom-right), the scorecard/setup "Auto play (test)"
# buttons, and letting the scavenger-hunt photo picker offer the phone's photo
# library (upload a saved image) instead of forcing the live camera. Defaults
# on; set to 'false' for production so players must take a real photo.
# NOTE: the hunt upload also pairs with the server's HUNT_ALLOW_PHOTO_OF_PHOTO
# (see server/.env.example) if you want screenshots/photos-of-screens to verify.
VITE_DEV_MODE=
